INSTALL for Developers
----------------------
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install build-essential cdbs devscripts dh-autoreconf intltool libgsf-1-dev libcairo2-dev libpango1.0-dev libxml2-dev libgirepository1.0-dev

./autogen.sh
make
sudo make install
sudo ldconfig


Making deb Package for end users
--------------------------------
cd libhwp
./autogen.sh # because of .po files
dch -l custom
dpkg-buildpackage -b
ls ..


Related Projects
----------------
